- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as social network analysis is mentioned as one of the application domains.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is mentioned as another application domain, and some of the high-level programming abstractions discussed in the paper are relevant to machine learning tasks.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses various graph processing algorithms and their implementations.
